title: Nowhere
alt: I mean, seriously, NOWHERE? For starters, there are like a thousand species of dinosaur.
transcript:
[Megan is sitting on a couch with Cueball lying in her lap.]
Cueball: There's nowhere 
Cueball: I'd rather be
Cueball: than with you
Cueball: here
Cueball: right now.[Silence.][Megan is imagining herself riding an apatosaurus.]
